CONTEXT
=======
INC Ransomware, infamous for attacking Yamaha Motors Philippines, Xerox and various Healthcare industries used multiple DLS websites on surface web to leak victims data.
INC Group had put their project for sale in May 2024 and rebranded as Lynx in July 2024
INC Ransomware DLS (100+ Victims) is still active along with Lynx Ransomware DLS (40 Victims)


